text: This was the first edition of the tournament. Robert Galloway and Nathaniel Lammons won the title after defeating Sander Gillé and Joran Vliegen 7–5, 6–4 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Oracle Challenger Series - New Haven - Men's Doubles
